{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "卓长卿与温瑾同行闯天目山第二关、第三关。在五芒神珠阵中，千里明驼牛一山欲杀多事头陀，卓长卿出手救人，反震之力令牛一山被五芒神珠击毙。无影罗刹萧铁风怒斥卓长卿假慈悲，温瑾以逻辑辩倒萧铁风，令其抱尸离去。玉郎毕四突然现身，此人乃花郎毕五之兄，竟当众向温瑾求婚，卓长卿怒喝制止。毕四暗发五棱钢针偷袭，卓长卿凭异衫毫发无损，反掷钢针令毕四狼狈滚避。温瑾欲割毕四鼻耳，卓长卿劝止放行。温如玉暗中现身，割下毕四鼻耳遣小玲、小琼送来，并邀温瑾与卓长卿晚间赴庙堂了断恩怨。小玲、小琼含泪与温瑾割袍断义，忠义两难令人唏嘘。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她倒想得周到得很。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "这也是那神偷乔迁的主意。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "武林群豪",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "姑娘倒早得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无根大师怎么与别人动起手来了——",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "萧大侠，你知道这是为了什么吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "speaker_name": "无影罗刹",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "这只是我们久仰少林绝技，是以才向无根大师讨教一下而已，别的没有什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "原来是这样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "但是这金刀换掌，和五芒神珠阵，可不是自己人考较武功的地方呀。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧铁风",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "只要大家手下留心些，也没有什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_yi_shan",
      "speaker_name": "千里明驼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这是自寻死路。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_wu_gen",
      "text": "大师，没有事吧？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_gen",
      "speaker_name": "多事头陀",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "兄弟，和尚今天服了你了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_wu_gen",
      "text": "大师言重了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧铁风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然死了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "也许有救，亦未可知。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧铁风",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "滚！滚开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "在下乃是一番好意，阁下何必如此！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧铁风",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "好意——哼哼，我从前听到猫抓死了老鼠，又去假哭，还不相信世上有此等情事，今日一见——哼哼，真教我好笑得很。我萧铁风又非三岁孩童，你这假慈悲骗得了谁！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "在下实在是一番好意，阁下如不相信……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "他不相信就算了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "我与此人，无冤无仇，此刻我无意伤了他的性命，心中实在不安……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "若是他伤了无根大师的性命呢？你是为了救人，又有谁会怪你？难道你应该袖手看着无根大师被他杀死么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧铁风",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "我不管你是真意假意，恶意好意，这牛一山总是被你给杀死的。此后牛一山的后代、子女、亲戚、朋友，会一个接着一个地找你复仇，直到眼看着你也像牛一山一样地死去为止。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "你既也是牛一山的朋友，想来也要代牛一山复仇了？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧铁风",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "为友报仇，自是天经地义之事……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "那么你若有此力量，你一定会代友报仇，将杀死你朋友的人杀死的了？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧铁风",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "这个自然！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "此人虽然杀死了你的朋友，但却与你无冤无仇，你为何要将人家杀死？这岂非是无理之极。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧铁风",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "这岂是无理？我代友复仇，这有理极了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "对了，你要代友复仇，所以能将一个与你素无冤仇的人杀死，而且自称极有道理，那么牛一山若是杀死了我们的朋友，我们再将他杀死，岂非是极有道理之事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "如此说来，牛一山立心要杀死我们的朋友，我们是以先将他杀死，而救出我们的朋友，难道就不是极有道理的事么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tie_feng",
      "text": "好好的将你朋友的尸身带走吧，还站在这里干什么！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "姑娘好厉害的口才，竟将一个罗刹说得抱头鼠窜而走，哈哈——当真是舌剑唇枪，锐如利刃，教我实在佩服得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "老夫来得真凑巧，虽未见着姑娘的身手，却已见到姑娘的口舌，当真是眼福不浅得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "恕我眼拙，老前辈……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "姑娘心里大约在奇怪，老夫是哪里来的。哈哈——老夫今晨偷偷摸摸地上山，一直到了这里，为的就是要大家吃上一惊。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "姑娘虽不认得老夫，老夫却认得姑娘的。老夫已久仰姑娘的美艳，更久仰姑娘的辣手，是以忍不住要到这天目山来走上一遭——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "你是花郎毕五的什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "姑娘果然眼光雪亮。不错——老夫毕四，便是那不成材的花郎毕五更不成材的哥哥。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "难道阁下便是人称玉郎的毕四先生么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "姑娘年纪轻轻，不但口才犀利，而且目中神光满盈，显见内功已有根基，难怪我那不成材的弟弟，要被姑娘削去鼻子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "那么阁下此来，莫非是要为令弟复仇的么，那么……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "不对，不对，不但不对，而且大错特错啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "那毕五又老又糊涂，自己不照照镜子，却想来吃天鹅肉，姑娘莫说削去他的鼻子，就算再削去他两只耳朵，老夫我不但不会反对，更不会为他复仇，只怕还要鼓掌赞成的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "请恕我无礼，方才多有冒犯之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "老前辈此来，可是为了家师……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "不是不是，非但不是，而且大错特错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "老夫不似毕五与令师还有三分交情，此来又怎会为了令师呢！若是……哈哈！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "那么老前辈此来，难道是游山玩水的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "美、美、真美！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "老前辈，你这是干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "你真的不知道么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "我真的不知道。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "你真的不知道……你真的不知道我的心么？……我正在向你求婚呀！我要你答应，答应嫁给我。我虽然是毕五的哥哥，却长得比他年轻，更比他英俊。你虽然拒绝了他，他活该，我想你一定不会拒绝我的，是吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "我当着别人跪在你面前，这表示我对你是多么痴情。你能伤害一个对你如此痴情的人的心吗？不会的，你是那么……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "住口！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "我说我的，干你何事？难道你在吃醋么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "站起来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "你是谁？你可知道老夫是谁？你竟敢在老夫面前这般放肆，哼哼，大约真的是活得有些不耐烦了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "我说话的对象是这位姑娘，只要这位姑娘愿意听，谁都不能叫我住口。你这小子算是什么！哼哼，当真是狗捉老鼠，多管闲事！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "姓毕的，你说了一堆废话，我却没有喝止，你知道是为了什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "想来是我的一片真心诚意，打动了姑娘的芳心，是以——",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "不对！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "那么可是姑娘听我说的十分好听，是以——",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "也不对！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "我小的时候，一个冬天的早上，正坐在院子里晒太阳，忽然有一条疯狗，跑来对我乱吠，我气不过，就把它打跑了，哪知我……我姑姑走来看见，却将我骂了一顿，说一个女孩子应该文静些，怎么可以和疯狗一般见识！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "是极，是极，姑娘今日这般文静，想必定是幼时教养极佳之故。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "我文静虽不见得，但却真的再也不和疯狗一般见识了，以后再有疯狗在我旁边狂吠，我只有走开一点，让让他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "可是现在如果有疯狗在我旁边狂吠，我就再也不必让他了，因为我现在已经有了……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "有了一个保护我的人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "长卿，你替我把这条疯狗赶走，好不好？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "你这小妮子，当真不识抬举，毕四太爷好意抬举你——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "我手掌三挥之后，你若还在此地，就莫怪我手下无情了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小子张狂，也要你见见毕四太爷的——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "还不快滚！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "你乱吠了半天，就这样想走了吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "你那宝贝弟弟，留下一只鼻子，你好歹也该留下一些东西来呀！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "是鼻子有用些，还是耳朵有用些？呀——想来两样都没有什么用，你还是两样都留下来吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "放他去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "我才不会和他一般见识哩，刚才不过是故意吓吓他的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "那就好了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "text": "还不快走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青山不改，绿水长流……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_lang_bi_si",
      "speaker_name": "毕四",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此恩此德，来日必报。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "你对他虽然这么仁慈，可是他却未必会感激你，说不定以后还要找你报仇也说不定。唉——那么你这又是何苦？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "做人但求自己无愧于心，至于别人怎样对我无所谓。哼哼，我岂是施恩望报之人——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "有些事你自然不会明了。唉——要是你从小就跟着我那恩师在一起，就不会——",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是玉郎毕四！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "这又是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "这可是那玉郎毕四的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小玲",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "这是祖姑姑叫我们交给姑娘的——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小玲",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "她老人家说，无论姑娘对她怎样，要是有人对姑娘无礼，她老人家还是不能坐视，所以——她老人家就代姑娘把这姓毕的鼻子和耳朵割下来，交给姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 635
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小玲",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "姑娘不接，我只得将它放在这里。反正只要姑娘知道，祖姑她老人家对姑娘还是那么关心就好了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiong",
      "speaker_name": "小琼",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "祖姑还叫我们告诉姑娘，姑娘若是想找她老人家报仇，她老人家一定会让姑娘称心如愿的。今天晚上，她老人家就在昨天晚上的庙堂里等候姑娘——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiong",
      "speaker_name": "小琼",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "她老人家还说，请这位卓相公，也和姑娘一起去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 657
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小玲",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "到时候，我们两人也会在那里等着姑娘的。我两人和姑娘从小在一起，承蒙姑娘看得起，没有把我们看成下人，我两人也一直感激得很，常常想以后一定要报答姑娘，可是——",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小玲",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "可是今天晚上，我两人再见姑娘之面的时候，却已是姑娘的仇人。姑娘若要对祖姑老人家怎样，那么就请姑娘也一样地对我们。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小玲",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "我们不像姑娘一样的博学多才，我们都笨得很。可是我们却也听说过一句话，那就是：人若以国士待我，我便以国士对人。这句话我不知说得对不对，但意思我却是懂的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiong",
      "speaker_name": "小琼",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "我们不管祖姑为人怎样，但她老人家一直对我们很好，就像她老人家一直对姑娘很好一样。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 677
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_jin",
      "speaker_name": "温瑾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "父母之仇，不共戴天。你两人这样说，我心里头虽然难受，但是——",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小玲",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "我们知道姑娘的心意，当然我们不能勉强，可是我也听说，古人有割袍断义、划地绝交的故事——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "小玲",
      "listener": "char_wen_jin",
      "text": "从此姑娘不要再认得我，我也不再认得姑娘了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiong",
      "speaker_name": "小琼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至此，我也再无话说。我想姑娘总比我们聪明得多，会选择一条该走的路，可是——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiong",
      "speaker_name": "小琼",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "卓相公，你是聪明人，我想问问你一句话，不知你可愿意听？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 715
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiong",
      "text": "且请说出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiong",
      "speaker_name": "小琼",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "生育之苦，固是为人子女者必报之恩，但养育之恩，难道就不是大恩么？难道就可以不报么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 722
    }
  ],
